1
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,130
After what happened today,

2
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,670
we can be certain that Cui Jun

3
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,920
wasn't abducted by Grand Tutor Xie.

4
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:55,580
Otherwise,

5
00:00:55,710 --> 00:00:57,240
he wouldn't have made a deal with me

6
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,920
just because of a letter from my mother.

7
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,350
If Cui Jun were in his hands,

8
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:02,150
he could have simply grilled him

9
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,600
for the truth behind
the An and Lu families' case.

10
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:06,590
I know your little brain
has become much sharper than before,

11
00:01:06,590 --> 00:01:08,050
but it needs some rest now.

12
00:01:08,430 --> 00:01:09,760
Stop thinking about it.

13
00:01:16,789 --> 00:01:17,680
Yummy.

14
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,000
Back when we were on the march,

15
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,200
all we could eat were
flatbreads or dried meat,

16
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:27,480
and occasionally finding some wild greens
would satisfy our cravings.

17
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,950
Now that you don't have
much of an appetite

18
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,430
and can't eat meat while in mourning,

19
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:31,830
you could try this first.

20
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:34,870
I've had wild-green flatbreads before,

21
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:37,070
but I've never had ones this delicious.

22
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:39,580
Surely Qing Long couldn't have made these.

23
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,130
Please thank Yan Yue for me.

24
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:48,120
Okay.

25
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,170
You are Crown Prince Wenxi.

26
00:01:54,509 --> 00:01:56,280
In terms of blood relations,

27
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,150
you should be

28
00:01:58,150 --> 00:02:00,480
the person closest to my mother
in this world.

29
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:03,010
Emperor Wenxi was my mother's
elder brother,

30
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,590
so you should call her...

31
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,200
Aunt.

32
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,940
But compared to me,

33
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,030
even though you aren't Princess Yunzhao's
biological daughter,

34
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:14,400
you are her true family.

35
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:19,600
There's no need for you to tell me that.

36
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:24,110
Blood ties are merely
where one comes from,

37
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,740
but not where one belongs.

38
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:29,750
A marriage brought about
by the pressure of the imperial family,

39
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:31,910
and one that had to be maintained
in order to bind the aristocratic clans

40
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:33,360
and the imperial family together,

41
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:36,840
ultimately wasted half the lives of
both Princess Yunzhao and Grand Tutor.

42
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,040
I hope that this time,

43
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:42,760
you can help Princess Yunzhao
find the freedom she deserved.

44
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,329
You sure sound convincing,

45
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,210
yet you're not exactly any better
yourself.

46
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,240
What?

47
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,590
I mean,

48
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,690
without any witnesses,

49
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:53,800
how can we bring the murderer

50
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,840
who killed my mother to justice?

51
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,710
Isn't there already a rumor going around

52
00:02:57,710 --> 00:03:00,710
that I killed Princess Yunzhao
to seize the Phoenix Heart Token?

53
00:03:00,710 --> 00:03:02,590
Let's fan the flames.

54
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:34,530
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

55
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:37,409
[Episode 18]

56
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:43,560
Since I harboured prejudices
against the An and Lu families,

57
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,310
I never truly listened to
what was in your heart,

58
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:47,940
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

59
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,960
thinking it was merely your obsession.

60
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:51,500
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

61
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:51,690
I always firmly believed
that you were the one who had wronged me,

62
00:04:51,690 --> 00:04:57,020
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

63
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:54,830
but I never realized
that I had wronged you as well.

64
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,630
I suspect that 25 years ago,

65
00:04:57,659 --> 00:05:01,100
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

66
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,130
the real Cui Jun had already been killed,

67
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:05,130
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

68
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:04,680
and that the man who survived
was a secret agent from Northern Qin.

69
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,750
If that's the case, then perhaps
there's more to

70
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:08,970
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

71
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:08,990
the An and Lu families' crime
he exposed back then than meets the eye.

72
00:05:08,990 --> 00:05:12,290
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

73
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,810
He refuses to speak now,

74
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,680
but I've brought him back to Jiankang.

75
00:05:12,810 --> 00:05:15,630
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

76
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,750
Whether or not I can clear
the An and Lu families' name,

77
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:18,150
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

78
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,720
at least this time,

79
00:05:18,410 --> 00:05:22,580
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

80
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,820
I'm standing with you.

81
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:26,200
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

82
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,380
We were once husband and wife.

83
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,560
May all past grievances be laid to rest,

84
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:28,220
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

85
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,680
and may you no longer be trapped
by the past.

86
00:05:28,450 --> 00:05:31,070
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

87
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,760
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

88
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:38,260
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

89
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:43,480
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

90
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,240
Grand Tutor.

91
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:04,040
I told you

92
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:07,330
about Li Mao's background

93
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,800
to warn you about the situation,

94
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:14,160
not so you could

95
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,310
kill my wife!

96
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:20,240
You're the one who truly fails to
understand the situation!

97
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,190
Crown Prince Wenxi isn't dead at all,

98
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:24,650
and they still have
the Phoenix Heart Token!

99
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,000
What did you say?

100
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,620
If Princess Yunzhao had returned alive,

101
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:39,159
my brother would have had
no chance of survival.

102
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,760
What other option did I have?

103
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:44,040
I wouldn't spare anyone

104
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,600
who might pose a threat to him.

105
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:51,360
Grand Tutor.

106
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,040
Mao.

107
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:20,510
Let's go.

108
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:35,430
What's this supposed to mean?

109
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:37,040
I said I'd give you this as a gift.

110
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,240
It's made of black iron,
which is even tougher than refined iron.

111
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,560
It won't rust or corrode for 100 years,

112
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:44,220
and it's 100 times more powerful
than Eagle King's Longque Blade.

113
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,000
When did you forge it?

114
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,720
Before we left for Guazhou.

115
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,720
But it didn't have a scabbard back then.

116
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,600
I specifically asked

117
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,950
Master Wei from Yunyan Pavilion

118
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,480
to craft one for this sword.

119
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,970
Well? Do you like it?

120
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,480
I'm sure

121
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:13,920
you wouldn't just give this to me
for nothing.

122
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:19,680
By the banks of the Qushui River,
there's a mountain called Mount Fengming.

123
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,070
It offers a broad view,

124
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,190
and when the weather is clear,

125
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,800
you can see the rolling mountain ranges.

126
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,930
Behind those ranges

127
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,720
lies my mother's former fief,

128
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,920
Yunzhao Prefecture.

129
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:32,490
Though, unfortunately, it later
fell under the control of Northern Qin.

130
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,440
So?

131
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,320
So I want to buy this mountain

132
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:37,270
and make it my mother's burial site.

133
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:37,960
However,

134
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:40,440
it is currently owned by
a wealthy local family,

135
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,510
and they're asking for a very high price.

136
00:08:41,510 --> 00:08:43,030
I've scraped together what I can,

137
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:45,160
but I'm still short by this little bit.

138
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:48,000
Don't worry, I'm not borrowing it
for free.

139
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,800
I've already paid you interest.

140
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,100
How much are you short?

141
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,400
Five thousand taels.

142
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,320
Don't tell me

143
00:08:58,150 --> 00:09:00,790
that the dignified Heir of Prince Jing'an,
commander of Beifu,

144
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,840
can't even come up with

145
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,900
a mere 5,000 taels.

146
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,440
My father owns a small forested mountain
on the outskirts of the capital.

147
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,150
The fengshui there is no worse than
that of Mount Fengming.

148
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:09,080
I'd be happy to
gift it to Princess Yunzhao.

149
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,650
If you don't want to lend it, just say so.

150
00:09:10,650 --> 00:09:12,650
Why go to all that trouble with lies?

151
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:37,830
Your Highness, why did you suddenly decide
to clean the horse today?

152
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,740
Your Highness, it's all here.

153
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,600
You've invested all your personal savings
in the army,

154
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:46,200
leaving only this small amount on you.

155
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,630
It's only a bit over 3,000 taels.

156
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:49,150
The dignified Heir of Prince Jing'an

157
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:51,120
only has 3,000 taels of personal savings—

158
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,380
no one would believe that if word got out.

159
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,210
Sell this red steed,

160
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,670
then exchange all of this for cash

161
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,530
and give it to He Yuanji.

162
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:01,030
Have her withdraw my entire share

163
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,150
from the family estate

164
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,600
and give it all to Xie Jiayu.

165
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,480
Just tell her it's a loan
from the Prince's household.

166
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,750
But this is the prized Western Regions
steed your father, His Highness, gave you,

167
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,960
1 in 10,000.

168
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,610
You won't find another one like it
in all of Ye.

169
00:10:11,610 --> 00:10:14,670
You wouldn't even bear
to ride it onto the battlefield.

170
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,750
Sell it.

171
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,150
Why didn't you try to talk him out of it?

172
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:39,880
Why should I?

173
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:42,720
Everything in this world has a price,
but affection is priceless.

174
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,520
Don't you know what matters more

175
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:45,630
in His Highness's heart?

176
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:47,240
Back when he used to toss money
to Master Yuan,

177
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,720
at least you could hear it clink.

178
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,240
Now he doesn't even reveal his name.

179
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:50,960
You fool.

180
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,480
Can't you think of a way

181
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,610
to let Lady Xie know?

182
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,080
Lady Xie?

183
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,790
I heard that when I was severely injured
after receiving a flogging,

184
00:10:58,790 --> 00:11:00,750
it was Your Highness who paid for
the purchase of precious medicinal herbs

185
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,710
to treat me.

186
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,000
It must have cost Your Highness a lot.

187
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,870
Since I can't pay you back right now,

188
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,960
I offer this deed of debt

189
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,800
as proof

190
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:10,770
that I'll surely repay the debt someday.

191
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,920
It was merely a small favor.

192
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,200
One should not accept rewards
without merit.

193
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,030
The life-saving kindness Your Highness
has shown me is far too great.

194
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,320
A great favor can become a burden
like an enemy's debt.

195
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,520
I'd rather bear a debt

196
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:21,830
than carry the weight of your kindness.

197
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,480
Sorry for offending you that day.

198
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,600
The distinction between nobles and commoners
and the differences in people's hearts...

199
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,320
You aristocratic traitors—

200
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:36,750
you're parasites feeding off our country!

201
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,630
Are not something a woman
like Your Highness could overcome.

202
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,960
I shouldn't have taken my anger out
on Your Highness.

203
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,020
I hereby apologize to Your Highness.

204
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,270
How do you plan

205
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,130
to pay this much money back?

206
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,840
By copying books,
or selling my calligraphy—

207
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,700
I'll find a way.

208
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,000
Let's go.

209
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:06,840
Qing Long?

210
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,840
Why are you taking the red steed
out of the mansion?

211
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,120
His Highness asked me to sell it.

212
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:11,720
Sell it?

213
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:13,790
Yes. His Highness told me
not to say anything.

214
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:16,520
Please pretend you didn't see it,
Your Highness.

215
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,360
Nanxing.

216
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:34,250
bring out my short dagger.

217
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,240
My Lady,

218
00:12:35,670 --> 00:12:36,870
but Her Highness

219
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,880
left it to you for self-defense.

220
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:41,450
I've got no choice. I'm broke.

221
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:43,320
Take these out and ask around
how much they're worth.

222
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,120
If the price is reasonable,
just pawn them all.

223
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:47,320
I'll figure out a way to make up the rest.

224
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,200
If we pawn Miraculous Craft as well,

225
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,390
it should probably be enough.

226
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:54,450
Is His Highness really unwilling
to lend you the money?

227
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,080
That's really stingy of him.

228
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,030
He's the commander of Beifu, after all.

229
00:12:59,030 --> 00:13:01,620
Didn't he just confiscate
the Cui family's mines?

230
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:03,030
Those were confiscated
on behalf of the court.

231
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,750
They're not
the Xiao family's private property.

232
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:06,080
Still, I never expected

233
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:08,790
Xiao Wuyi wouldn't even lend me
5,000 taels.

234
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:10,450
I thought he would at least...

235
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:11,360
Xie Jiayu,

236
00:13:12,510 --> 00:13:13,710
I'm smitten with you.

237
00:13:14,910 --> 00:13:16,970
Talking about being smitten with me.

238
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:18,150
Forget it.

239
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,990
In the end, I only have myself to rely on.

240
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:25,480
Yuanji.

241
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:30,720
This is...

242
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,720
I'm lending this to you
on behalf of Prince Jing'an's Household.

243
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,440
Take it and choose any place you like

244
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,550
as Princess Yunzhao's burial site.

245
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,630
The Heir has been fighting battles
all over the country these past years.

246
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:38,670
Although he hasn't spent much on himself,

247
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,440
Beifu's expenditures have been enormous.

248
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,700
He's poured all his salary into the army.

249
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:44,120
The expenses of Prince Jing'an's Household

250
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,200
have been completely supported
by me and the Princess Consort.

251
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,550
We truly cannot count on
the Heir and Prince Jing'an.

252
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:50,630
I oversee
Prince Jing'an's Household's accounts,

253
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,690
and the Heir is indeed short on funds.

254
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,780
I'm being completely honest.

255
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,910
Then where did this money come from?

256
00:13:58,340 --> 00:14:00,460
The Heir had Ferghana horse.

257
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,200
I heard it was a gift from Prince Jing'an

258
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,810
when he won his first battle.

259
00:14:04,810 --> 00:14:07,320
That horse had a pure bloodline
and was priceless.

260
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,550
A few days ago, I saw Qing Long

261
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,810
lead it away to be sold,

262
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,910
along with some land deeds and shop deeds.

263
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:14,240
All together, this is how much was raised.

264
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,360
The Heir even kept it from me too.

265
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:18,420
He only told me to send the money over.

266
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,480
Do you know what the two largest expenses

267
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,150
under the Heir's name in the household

268
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,870
were in the past year?

269
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:25,670
What?

270
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:28,190
The first was your wedding with the Heir—

271
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:31,520
a fake wedding doomed to be ruined
from the start.

272
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,390
Well, a fake act has to be made

273
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:36,870
convincing enough
for people to believe it, right?

274
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:39,480
The second was the renovation

275
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:42,390
of this Cangfeng Forge
after you moved into the mansion.

276
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:43,480
This place used to be nothing more than

277
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:45,200
an empty room for storing sundries,

278
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,400
abandoned for years.

279
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,360
Didn't you notice

280
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:51,490
that the furnace outside
was also renovated?

281
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:56,670
No wonder.

282
00:14:57,790 --> 00:15:00,450
No wonder it looks so much like
the one at my home.

283
00:15:13,790 --> 00:15:14,510
Xiao Wuyi,

284
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,920
you sold your horse,

285
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,940
but you didn't take the interest.

286
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:22,840
Qing Long...

287
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,150
But this is not

288
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:32,000
what I want.

289
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:42,870
What do you want then?

290
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,240
I'm not telling you.

291
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:54,790
I don't want you to think of this

292
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:55,790
as a transaction.

293
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:01,650
Your Highness.

294
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,290
The Empress Dowager is hosting a banquet.

295
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:06,360
Under what pretext?

296
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,320
She claims

297
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,120
Empress Wenxi

298
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:10,600
appeared in her dream,

299
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:13,870
asking Your Highness to bring
the Phoenix Heart Token into the palace.

300
00:16:13,870 --> 00:16:14,600
All right.

301
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:16,550
She finally couldn't hold back any longer

302
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:18,080
and came forward on her own.

303
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:30,240
Mother!

304
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,320
Mother!

305
00:16:33,670 --> 00:16:35,790
Why do people like you, high and mighty,

306
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:37,480
always try to corner me and my brother?

307
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:39,150
We simply want to survive.

308
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,490
Your Highness.

309
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:41,870
My brother has been so kind to Yaoyao.

310
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,790
Why are you still unwilling to let him go?

311
00:16:43,790 --> 00:16:44,750
Calm down!

312
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,410
I never wanted Prince Qi dead!

313
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:47,720
You hold the Phoenix Heart Token,

314
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,670
and you intend to support
Crown Prince Wenxi.

315
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:51,000
If he ever makes it to Jiankang,

316
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,600
will my brother
have any chance of survival?

317
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,150
Tell me,

318
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,200
where exactly
is Crown Prince Wenxi hiding?

319
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,030
There's no way I'll tell you that!

320
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:59,000
Fine. Then let's take this secret with us

321
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:00,120
and vanish

322
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,000
from this world together!

323
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,000
Mao...

324
00:17:20,069 --> 00:17:20,680
Lejun.

325
00:17:22,349 --> 00:17:23,280
Don't be afraid.

326
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:27,400
Mao...

327
00:17:33,550 --> 00:17:34,160
Mao.

328
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,110
Do you remember

329
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:39,030
when we were little,

330
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:41,850
wandering among displaced refugees?

331
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:43,510
Back then,

332
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:46,270
whenever there was a single flatbread

333
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,470
or a bowl of porridge,

334
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:50,030
you'd always let me have it.

335
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,800
Whenever older children tried to bully me,

336
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:02,000
you'd risk your life to protect me.

337
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,820
Those memories aren't pleasant.

338
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:06,490
I've long forgotten them.

339
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,270
But I haven't.

340
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:13,310
Although those days were harsh,

341
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:16,350
they were the happiest time

342
00:18:17,370 --> 00:18:18,410
of my life.

343
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:21,590
Because even back then,

344
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:25,400
I knew I had the best older brother
in the entire world—

345
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:31,830
one who'd never let go of my hand,

346
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,640
not even in death.

347
00:18:36,110 --> 00:18:36,920
Mao.

348
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:40,000
I wasn't afraid then,

349
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:42,830
and I'm even less afraid now.

350
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:44,440
Mao.

351
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:48,090
I will protect you, no matter what.

352
00:18:58,750 --> 00:18:59,640
It's alright.

353
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,200
Don't be afraid.

354
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:17,590
Yaoyao.

355
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,870
Greetings, Princess Pingning.

356
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:25,440
Yaoyao.

357
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,350
Are you truly determined

358
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:28,750
to draw a line between us?

359
00:19:29,910 --> 00:19:30,680
Her Highness...

360
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:32,270
Other than an admission of guilt,

361
00:19:32,270 --> 00:19:33,680
I never want to hear another word

362
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:35,410
about my mother from your lips.

363
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,340
We were once good friends.

364
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:40,960
There's no need for
such hollow pretenses between us.

365
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:45,960
Yaoyao.

366
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:49,290
You've truly grown up.

367
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:52,320
It's all because of you
that I had to grow up.

368
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,790
Do you really think

369
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:55,250
your scheme was flawless?

370
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:57,110
That day,

371
00:19:58,270 --> 00:20:00,400
Her Highness and I
both fell off the cliff.

372
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,030
If not for a tree that caught me,

373
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,750
I wouldn't have survived, either.

374
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:06,010
And it was Young Lord Xiao's men saved me.

375
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:09,030
M-My hand had only just healed.

376
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:12,000
To accuse me of
trying to harm Princess Yunzhao

377
00:20:12,850 --> 00:20:14,110
is rather absurd.

378
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:15,570
If that's the case,

379
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:18,350
then why did you have Da
snatch the coachman's family

380
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,880
from me?

381
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,590
Were you afraid

382
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,250
they witnessed something
they shouldn't have?

383
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,620
But they didn't see anything.

384
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,550
Lejun.

385
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,160
I truly hope it wasn't you.

386
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:40,030
Because if it was,

387
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:43,000
I'd be deeply disappointed
in our friendship.

388
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:44,400
Yaoyao.

389
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,750
I didn't expect you
to enter the palace today.

390
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:53,440
Mao.

391
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,070
You knew I was using you

392
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:56,030
to test Li Lejun.

393
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,740
She's your sister.

394
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:00,350
I believe you only learned about it
afterwards.

395
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:02,640
I understand that
you were put in a difficult position.

396
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,640
I don't blame you.

397
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:07,850
But please, don't make things difficult
for me anymore either.

398
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:57,400
Long live Your Majesty!

399
00:21:57,590 --> 00:21:58,830
You may rise, my beloved ministers.

400
00:21:58,830 --> 00:22:00,480
Thank you, Your Majesty!

401
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,170
Today, at this palace banquet,

402
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:08,260
I'd like to raise a toast with
all my beloved ministers.

403
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:19,480
A few days ago, Empress Wenxi
appeared to me in a dream,

404
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,750
and I've learned
that the old prophecy—

405
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:23,240
"when the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world"—

406
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,200
is no mere tale.

407
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:25,940
Two Phoenix Heart Tokens have been

408
00:22:25,940 --> 00:22:29,200
passed down to Princess Yunzhao
and Cui Jun respectively.

409
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:34,610
That's enough.

410
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:38,480
My Lord,

411
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:41,070
what's the point of arresting me?

412
00:22:41,070 --> 00:22:42,680
I'm a useless wreck now.

413
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:46,510
The Phoenix Heart Token
is in Xiao Wuyi's hands.

414
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,930
Young Lord Xiao.

415
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:51,510
It's been quite some time
since you returned from Guazhou.

416
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:55,110
When will the convicted criminal Cui
be transferred to the Court of Judicial Review?

417
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:57,310
And where is the Phoenix Heart Token?

418
00:22:58,030 --> 00:22:58,830
Your Majesty.

419
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:01,510
Cui Jun was abducted.

420
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:04,710
When did this happen?

421
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:06,240
And where was he abducted?

422
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:09,780
It was 5 days ago.

423
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,200
I'm still searching for him.

424
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,570
He was abducted 5 days ago,

425
00:23:12,570 --> 00:23:13,960
so why didn't you report it?

426
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:16,000
Do you have any regard for the laws of Ye?

427
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:16,830
Or could it be that

428
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,490
you hid Cui Jun away yourself—

429
00:23:18,510 --> 00:23:20,790
just like how you silenced
Princess Yunzhao

430
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:22,400
and stole her Phoenix Heart Token?

431
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:24,510
Vice Minister Qi, you seem eager
to pin a crime on me.

432
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:26,350
I have long submitted a memorial
confessing my fault

433
00:23:26,350 --> 00:23:28,080
over Cui Jun's disappearance.

434
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:31,500
Deliver this memorial to
the Department of State Affairs.

435
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:34,240
Remember, slip it in
among the daily greetings memorials

436
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:35,110
so it draws no attention.

437
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:35,840
Understood.

438
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:38,590
I know the Cui Family Case
is of great importance,

439
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:41,000
but I haven't heard anything
from the Department of State Affairs.

440
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,330
I was wondering myself—

441
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:43,750
how is it that Cui Jun has disappeared,

442
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,270
yet the court doesn't seem concerned
at all?

443
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:46,880
As a witness in the Cui Family Case,

444
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:49,480
I've been waiting for
the court deliberation.

445
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:50,880
Vice Minister Qi.

446
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:53,160
You've gone and accused me of
silencing Princess Yunzhao.

447
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,560
Do you have any evidence?

448
00:23:54,890 --> 00:23:56,270
Might I charge you with
lodging a false accusation?

449
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:56,790
You...

450
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,070
Anyway, Cui Jun disappeared
while he was in your custody.

451
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:03,200
Enough. You are both
loyal and righteous ministers.

452
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,350
There is no need to blame each other.

453
00:24:04,350 --> 00:24:05,680
Your Majesty, what I mean is that

454
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:07,960
Young Lord Xiao deliberately concealed
the Phoenix Heart Token's whereabouts.

455
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:09,550
Now that Princess Yunzhao fell dead

456
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:10,920
and Cui Jun has disappeared
without a trace,

457
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:13,000
if it weren't for Empress Wenxi
appearing to you in a dream,

458
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:13,960
we would all

459
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,620
remain kept in the dark by him.

460
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:17,700
I believe there's definitely more to

461
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:20,310
Princess Yunzhao's death
than meets the eye.

462
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:23,550
I respectfully request that Your Majesty
conduct a thorough investigation.

463
00:24:23,550 --> 00:24:24,480
Grand Tutor Xie.

464
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:25,400
Since Vice Minister Qi insists

465
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:27,110
there's more to Princess Yunzhao's death,

466
00:24:27,110 --> 00:24:29,070
would you support a thorough investigation

467
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:31,200
to seek justice for Princess Yunzhao?

468
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,080
If there is evidence,

469
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:38,230
then naturally it should be investigated.

470
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,550
Since this is merely an accusation

471
00:24:39,550 --> 00:24:40,550
with no evidence,

472
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:43,940
let's put the matter of Princess Yunzhao
aside for now.

473
00:24:44,110 --> 00:24:45,040
Young Lord Xiao.

474
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,400
Do you have Cui Jun's Phoenix Heart Token
in your possession?

475
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,260
Don't tell me it was snatched away

476
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,600
along with Cui Jun when he was abducted.

477
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:53,870
No, it wasn't.

478
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,530
The Phoenix Heart Token

479
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:57,600
is indeed in my possession.

480
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:01,970
So it's in his possession?

481
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,550
Is that the Phoenix Heart Token?

482
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,480
Everyone, please take a look.

483
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:16,310
This is the Phoenix Heart Token
that Cui Jun had.

484
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:18,240
So this is the Phoenix Heart Token?

485
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:21,030
I wonder if when Empress Wenxi
appeared in your dream,

486
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:23,690
was this the piece she showed you,
Your Majesty?

487
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,920
Since you all wish to see it so badly,

488
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,180
why not pass it around?

489
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:41,350
It doesn't seem all that special.

490
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,310
Isn't this just an ordinary token?
How could it deserve the saying

491
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:48,000
"when the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world"?

492
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:50,350
It is said the Cui family's private mines

493
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:53,960
were discovered
because of this Phoenix Heart Token.

494
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,400
In your opinion, Young Lord Xiao,

495
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:11,070
after Cui Jun has finally been
brought to justice

496
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:15,670
after having committed
countless crimes,
who should this Token be handed over to?

497
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:24,050
Did Empress Wenxi not mention this

498
00:26:24,050 --> 00:26:26,000
to Your Majesty when she appeared
in your dream?

499
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,110
"Under Heaven,

500
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:29,090
all land belongs to the ruler;

501
00:26:29,090 --> 00:26:30,170
within the realm,

502
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:31,640
all people are the ruler's subjects.

503
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:34,100
Yet unfair divisions burden the officials,

504
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:40,000
while I alone toil tirelessly.

505
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:47,110
Praise that I am not yet worn with age,

506
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:48,640
still strong and vigorous.

507
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:51,920
With robust strength,
I oversee all corners of the realm."

508
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:53,750
I hope Your Majesty will have sympathy for
the Beifu troops

509
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:55,400
who fight without regard for their lives,

510
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:57,260
yet suffer from shoddy weaponry.

511
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,510
I respectfully request
that the copper and iron mines

512
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:00,790
confiscated from
the Cui family's private mines

513
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:02,450
be allocated to the Beifu Army

514
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:04,080
to upgrade their armaments.

515
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,140
Please rise, Young Lord Xiao.

516
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,880
What you speak makes perfect sense.

517
00:27:12,550 --> 00:27:14,920
The Beifu soldiers are warriors
of our great Ye.

518
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:17,270
I approved your Beifu Reform

519
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:20,110
precisely to forge
a more elite, formidable army.

520
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:23,170
Moreover, you've rendered
meritorious service

521
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:25,000
in cracking the Cui Family Case
and deserve a reward.

522
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,480
I find your request

523
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:28,310
most reasonable.

524
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:31,410
The Cui family's private mines
shall be dedicated to

525
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:34,090
upgrading the Beifu Army's weaponry.

526
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:38,630
On behalf of the Beifu soldiers,

527
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:41,300
I thank Your Majesty for
your benevolent grace.

528
00:27:44,310 --> 00:27:45,200
Xiao Wuyi!

529
00:27:46,310 --> 00:27:47,530
How dare you mock me?

530
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,350
Where's the Phoenix Heart Token?

531
00:27:49,350 --> 00:27:50,240
How could this be?

532
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,270
How come it's empty?

533
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,160
I have no idea.

534
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:53,440
The Phoenix Heart Token

535
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:55,440
was right here in this brocade box
just moments ago.

536
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,500
All the officials in the court saw it.

537
00:27:57,790 --> 00:27:58,750
-Yeah, we all saw it.
-How could it be gone?

538
00:27:58,750 --> 00:27:59,680
There's no way.

539
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,240
Exactly.

540
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:09,040
Everyone saw it.
It needs to be thoroughly investigated.

541
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:09,870
Your Majesty.

542
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,590
I noticed

543
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:13,970
that when His Highness turned around,

544
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:16,510
Princess Pingning
stole the Phoenix Heart Token.

545
00:28:16,510 --> 00:28:18,400
I didn't! You're slandering me!

546
00:28:18,590 --> 00:28:20,830
Doing that in front of everyone here—
do you think I'm crazy?

547
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:23,760
Whether you have it or not,
we'll know after a search.

548
00:28:25,090 --> 00:28:25,770
Search her.

549
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:29,040
Your Majesty!

550
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:31,680
I didn't...

551
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,750
I didn't. I...

552
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,520
It was really on her. It really was.

553
00:28:38,720 --> 00:28:39,520
Your Majesty!

554
00:28:39,750 --> 00:28:41,680
Your Majesty, that's impossible!

555
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:43,170
I was framed.

556
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,270
I-I didn't take it!

557
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:57,760
Your Majesty.

558
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,510
May I borrow the brocade box?

559
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,790
Granted.

560
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:17,410
There's a hidden compartment?

561
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:19,590
You...

562
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:20,550
That's right.

563
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:22,630
You didn't take Cui Jun's token.

564
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:25,000
Because the one that fell out of you

565
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,510
was my mother's.

566
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,360
Princess Yunzhao's?

567
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:32,920
Why did she have
Princess Yunzhao's token?

568
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:33,510
Exactly.

569
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,680
Please forgive me, Your Majesty,

570
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,590
for contriving this contraption
to conceal the Phoenix Heart Token

571
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:38,480
and deceiving you.

572
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,880
I did so only to retrieve the token
on Princess Pingning

573
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:43,540
and uncover the truth
behind my mother's death.

574
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,640
I'm innocent.

575
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:49,550
That Phoenix Heart Token
didn't belong to Princess Yunzhao.

576
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:50,800
What makes you say so?

577
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:54,150
Could it be that
you've seen my mother's token?

578
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:54,910
When?

579
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,200
Li Lejun.

580
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:11,270
You murdered Princess Yunzhao
for the Phoenix Heart Token.

581
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,480
The Phoenix Heart Token on you

582
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,880
is the most compelling evidence
of your guilt.

583
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:14,940
It's not like that.

584
00:30:15,590 --> 00:30:16,250
It's not...

585
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,200
It seems

586
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:22,650
Princess Yunzhao's death
is indeed suspicious.

587
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:25,920
It's fake.

588
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,810
That Phoenix Heart Token is fake.

589
00:30:27,810 --> 00:30:29,420
It was forged, Your Majesty!

590
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,480
Your Majesty.

591
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:32,960
I've heard that the Phoenix Heart Tokens

592
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,830
were cast from the Phoenix Imperial Seal

593
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:35,830
of Empress Wenxi.

594
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:37,440
Though the carvings can be replicated,

595
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,310
the unique material of
the Phoenix Imperial Seal

596
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,400
cannot be faked.

597
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,400
Whether it's genuine or not,

598
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:44,200
we need only compare
the two Phoenix Heart Tokens.

599
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:56,280
Cui Jun's, Prince Jing'an's.

600
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:58,350
And this one...

601
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:06,550
This one belongs to Crown Prince Wenxi.

602
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,060
The engraving on it

603
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,280
was carved by my mother herself.

604
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:15,170
This one is the "Phoenix Head" token.

605
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:19,060
It holds command over
the other 3 Phoenix Heart Tokens.

606
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:21,880
Are you truly willing to take out
one of the tokens

607
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:23,680
to play along with me in this act?

608
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,550
Right now, the world only knows of

609
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:26,790
the 2 tokens held by
Cui Jun and my mother.

610
00:31:26,790 --> 00:31:28,920
They have no idea
that the rest are in your possession.

611
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,980
Once you reveal it,

612
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:32,790
at the very least Grand Tutor and Li Mao
will learn that

613
00:31:32,790 --> 00:31:34,990
Prince Jing'an was also a token holder.

614
00:31:35,510 --> 00:31:36,460
Your identity

615
00:31:37,310 --> 00:31:38,310
might be exposed.

616
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:41,060
What goes around comes around.

617
00:31:41,060 --> 00:31:43,000
Debts of gratitude and vengeance
must be repaid.

618
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:44,600
It's just a token, after all.

619
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:46,950
If it can bring the murderer to justice,

620
00:31:47,390 --> 00:31:48,450
then it's worth it.

621
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,110
It's indeed genuine.

622
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,110
No way.

623
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:00,510
No way...

624
00:32:04,030 --> 00:32:04,920
It was you.

625
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:08,410
Xiao Wuyi, so you also have
a Phoenix Heart Token.

626
00:32:09,770 --> 00:32:10,900
Princess Pingning,

627
00:32:11,790 --> 00:32:13,250
what do you mean by "also"?

628
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:16,130
That Phoenix Heart Token is yours.

629
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,510
You used your own token

630
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:19,030
to help Jiayu frame me.

631
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,070
Princess Pingning,

632
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:24,930
do you truly think I, Xiao Wuyi,
am some kind of saint

633
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,570
Everyone knows that

634
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:29,350
the Phoenix Heart Tokens contain secrets
about hidden mineral deposits.

635
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:30,950
Tell me, which one of you here

636
00:32:31,000 --> 00:32:32,130
would not want them?

637
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:34,410
If I had a Phoenix Heart Token,

638
00:32:34,550 --> 00:32:35,680
why wouldn't I keep it hidden

639
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,200
and secretly mine the resources?

640
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,160
Why would I bring it out
in front of all the court officials

641
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,400
just to frame you?

642
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,050
Who do you think you are?

643
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,510
I'd like to ask all of you present:

644
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,680
does anyone truly believe I, Xiao Wuyi,

645
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:47,610
would be so selfless and generous?

646
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:52,510
Your Majesty,
besides the Phoenix Heart Token,

647
00:32:52,510 --> 00:32:53,710
I also have a witness.

648
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:55,650
Summon them.

649
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:05,270
This is Ms. Yang, the coachman's wife.

650
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:06,930
They saw nothing to begin with

651
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,790
and were no witnesses at all.

652
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:10,440
But after you abducted them,

653
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:13,480
they ended up becoming witnesses
against you.

654
00:33:14,110 --> 00:33:14,750
She...

655
00:33:15,110 --> 00:33:16,880
She asked me where I was

656
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:19,440
between 3 to 4 a.m.
on the day of the incident,

657
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:21,110
and whether I had been to the stable.

658
00:33:21,110 --> 00:33:22,680
After learning that
I had not yet gotten up,

659
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,920
she asked no further questions.

660
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:25,640
That must've been the very hour
you snuck into the stables

661
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,300
to slip the poison, wasn't it?

662
00:33:31,030 --> 00:33:31,750
Let's go.

663
00:33:41,340 --> 00:33:42,010
Wait.

664
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:47,040
Don't commit any more killing.

665
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:03,350
I really should've killed them all.

666
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:06,030
Princess Pingning murdered my mother

667
00:34:06,030 --> 00:34:07,890
to seize the Phoenix Heart Token.

668
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:11,170
Please seek justice for my mother,
Your Majesty.

669
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:13,920
Your Majesty.

670
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,710
These pieces of evidence are not enough
to convict Lejun.

671
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:16,960
Further investigation is needed.

672
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,440
Please deliberate this matter
with caution, Your Majesty.

673
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,840
Prince Qi, are you trying

674
00:34:20,070 --> 00:34:22,000
to cover up for Princess Pingning?

675
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:34,030
If Princess Pingning truly feels wronged,

676
00:34:34,550 --> 00:34:38,190
we might as well have the entire
Eastern Palace thoroughly searched

677
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,670
to prove her innocence.

678
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,199
Your Majesty.

679
00:34:45,330 --> 00:34:46,530
-Your Majesty!
-I...

680
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:49,010
I plead guilty.

681
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:49,840
Lejun!

682
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,699
I plead guilty.

683
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:52,630
It was me.

684
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:56,150
I murdered Princess Yunzhao

685
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:58,370
to seize her Phoenix Heart Token.

686
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,950
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

687
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:16,550
He Tian.

688
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:17,360
Guards.

689
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,630
That day,

690
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:28,280
you suddenly had a stomachache
and needed to lie down.

691
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,880
I was the one who drugged you.

692
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:32,700
What's wrong?

693
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:33,920
Mother,

694
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,330
I feel a little unwell.

695
00:35:36,070 --> 00:35:38,480
Your Highness,
why don't we share a ride?

696
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:40,630
I spared you

697
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:43,810
only because I did not wish
to drag you into this.

698
00:35:44,110 --> 00:35:45,710
If I had been ruthless enough

699
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:50,140
to strike directly at your carriage
with Princess Yunzhao inside

700
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:52,330
and send both of you to your deaths,

701
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:59,320
none of this would have happened today,
would it?

702
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:09,280
Lejun!

703
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:50,470
Your Majesty.

704
00:36:51,590 --> 00:36:53,630
Princess Yunzhao did not die
as a criminal.

705
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,440
This token

706
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:56,400
was left to her by Empress Wenxi.

707
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,360
Now that she's passed away

708
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,920
and had divorced Grand Tutor Xie,

709
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,800
this token

710
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:04,110
should rightfully be inherited
by her offspring.

711
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:06,240
So, according to you, Young Lord Xiao,

712
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:07,550
-we should...
-The whereabouts of the remaining

713
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:09,800
Phoenix Heart Tokens are still unknown.

714
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,840
If Your Majesty were to claim them
all for yourself

715
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,670
in front of the entire court,

716
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:15,710
I'm afraid the remaining token holders

717
00:37:15,710 --> 00:37:17,170
would never come forward.

718
00:37:20,150 --> 00:37:23,350
As for whether it should go to
Grand Tutor Xie or Xie Jiayu—

719
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,140
the choice is Your Majesty's.

720
00:37:35,030 --> 00:37:36,280
Come to me.

721
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,360
Good girl.

722
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:50,140
You've really been through a lot.

723
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,480
Your devotion to capturing
the murderer who killed your mother

724
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:55,190
speaks volumes of your filial piety.

725
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,590
This Phoenix Heart Token

726
00:37:57,110 --> 00:38:00,190
was originally left to Princess Yunzhao
by Empress Wenxi.

727
00:38:00,190 --> 00:38:01,720
Now that she's passed away,

728
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,870
it's only right that you keep it.

729
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:11,360
Thank you for your gracious kindness,
Your Majesty.

730
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:13,760
Should the secrets of
the Phoenix Heart Token ever be uncovered,

731
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:17,090
I'll present this token to our great Ye
without hesitation.

732
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:19,280
What a good girl.

733
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:23,630
From now on, come to the palace
more often with Yuanji.

734
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:26,650
Yes, Your Majesty.

735
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:48,550
Xiao Wuyi.

736
00:38:51,060 --> 00:38:52,360
You forced me to personally send

737
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,690
my own sister to prison.

738
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:55,770
She committed murder,

739
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:59,440
and the victim was none other than
Xie Jiayu's mother.

740
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:01,570
You know perfectly well why she did it.

741
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:04,250
She did it to protect me.

742
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,360
Protect you?

743
00:39:06,710 --> 00:39:09,480
You both live in fear of
Crown Prince Wenxi's return,

744
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,320
but Crown Prince Wenxi

745
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,230
died 20 years ago!

746
00:39:14,070 --> 00:39:16,190
If it weren't for Princess Yunzhao
saving Li Lejun with her medical skills,

747
00:39:16,190 --> 00:39:18,480
Li Lejun's condition would never
have improved,

748
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,610
and she wouldn't have lived until now.

749
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:22,630
And yet, because of a little suspicion,

750
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,670
a fleeting fear,

751
00:39:23,670 --> 00:39:25,440
she could raise her blade against
the very person who saved her.

752
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:27,570
Tell me, did Li Lejun do nothing wrong?

753
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,640
Once she chose to act,

754
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:32,670
she must bear the consequences.

755
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:34,060
Li Yizhi, as the Regent,

756
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:36,820
you're supposed to know right from wrong

757
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:37,760
and where the line must be drawn!

758
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:39,340
Right from wrong?

759
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:42,550
Do you dare say that you helped Xie Jiayu

760
00:39:42,550 --> 00:39:44,210
without any selfish motives?

761
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:54,440
How insolent of you.

762
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:57,240
You know how much I couldn't bear
to part with Yaoyao.

763
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:59,380
Now that you've driven my sister
into jail,

764
00:39:59,380 --> 00:40:01,630
you still expect me to continue
being friends with you

765
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:03,360
and push forward with the reform together?

766
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:04,800
No such easy bargain exists

767
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:05,920
in this world!

768
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,680
Your Highness Prince Qi!

769
00:40:10,070 --> 00:40:12,030
If you must find someone to blame

770
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:14,170
to make yourself feel better,

771
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,230
you can hate me.

772
00:40:16,670 --> 00:40:17,400
But Li Yizhi,

773
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:22,390
you, too, rose from the ranks of
the displaced commoners.

774
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:25,490
Since you've chosen to
sit in this position,

775
00:40:26,550 --> 00:40:28,150
you should have a more compassionate heart

776
00:40:28,150 --> 00:40:29,610
and broader aspirations.

777
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:31,850
The road ahead is long.

778
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:35,020
Do not let fear and desire consume you

779
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:38,530
and make you forget
the path you once walked.

780
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:04,080
Is Crown Prince Wenxi

781
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:07,480
really dead?

782
00:41:16,630 --> 00:41:17,440
He's dead.

783
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:20,480
He died long ago,

784
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,400
and he'll never come back.
